pre_pr_migrator_status.python39: not solvable: ['win_64_numpy1.19python3.9.____cpython: Encountered problems while solving.\nProblem: nothing provides vc 10.* needed by python-3.4.5-0\n']

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "xrayutilities" %}
{% set version = "1.7.4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b8a6bc741273eaf10daea6862e4c84123feffe349c1e40bb55af1e858059a683

build:
  number: 1
  script: '{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv '
  skip: true  # [py2k]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - numpy
    - pip
    - setuptools
    - python
    - h5py
    - scipy
  run:
    - h5py
    - matplotlib-base
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - python
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - xrayutilities
    - xrayutilities.analysis
    - xrayutilities.io
    - xrayutilities.materials
    - xrayutilities.math
    - xrayutilities.simpack

about:
  home: https://xrayutilities.sourceforge.io
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: package for x-ray diffraction data evaluation
  doc_url: https://xrayutilities.sourceforge.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/dkriegner/xrayutilities

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
    - dkriegner
